#upgrade-account-modal.medium.reveal-modal data-reveal=""
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      h3.upgrade-account-modal-title style="margin-bottom: 20px;"
        | Upgrade your account
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      .row
        .small-12.large-6.columns
          .remove-after-pay
            .upgrade-feature-holder
              .top-row
                span.icon-holder
                  i.fa.fa-trophy
                span.upgrade-account-modal-text
                  | Guaranteed win
                i.fa.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.upgrade-account-icon.check-mark-icon

              .bottom-row
                p
                  | Instead of entering a draw, upgraded users are guaranteed to win rewards on a first come first serve basis. If you really want to meet someone, this is the way to go! The same hours verification and donor approval rules apply.

        .small-12.large-6.columns
          .remove-after-pay
            .upgrade-feature-holder
              .top-row
                span.icon-holder
                  i.fa.fa-calendar
                span.upgrade-account-modal-text
                  | Longer history
                i.fa.fa-check-circle.fa-2x.upgrade-account-icon.check-mark-icon

              .bottom-row
                p
                  | Free accounts count volunteer hours only from the past 60 days while upgraded accounts count volunteer hours from up to one year ago. This is helpful if you're a busy person who can only volunteer a few hours here and there.

      .button.secondary.upgrade-billing-period-button.remove-after-pay.selected-billing-period-button data-billing-type="annual" style="margin-right: 10px;"
        .upgrade-price-in-button
          | $7 / month
        .upgrade-text-in-button
          | Annual billing

      .button.secondary.upgrade-billing-period-button.remove-after-pay.not-selected-billing-period-button data-billing-type="monthly"
        .upgrade-price-in-button
          | $10 / month
        .upgrade-text-in-button
          | Monthly billing

      .hide-for-small-only
        .billing-bubble
          | Save 30% per year

      - message_beside_button = "You can cancel at any time. Read about our simple refund policy #{link_to 'here', faq_path(:anchor => 'general'), :target => '_blank'}."

      h5
        b.upgrade-details-bold-text

      .upgrade-action-holder
        script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js"
        .button.alert.remove-after-pay id="upgradeButton" data-url="#{upgrade_details_path}" style="margin-right: 10px;"
          | Upgrade
        span.upgrade-price.remove-after-pay
          .show-for-large-up
            = message_beside_button.html_safe
        div.upgrade-price.remove-after-pay.hide-for-large-up
          = message_beside_button.html_safe

        .commit-clock-loader.hide
          = image_tag "clock-loader.gif"

      hr

  .row
    .small-12.columns
      .no-thanks-on-premium.right.remove-after-pay
        | No thanks - I'll pass for now.
      

